			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64641064" name="comment_link_64641064" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23394474&amp;cid=64641064" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64641064)" >Re:</a>


